    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Rapid assessment of the transmission potential of an emerging or reemerging pathogen is a cornerstone of public health response. A simple approach is shown for using the number of disease introductions and secondary cases to determine whether the upper bound of the reproduction number exceeds the critical value of one.</jats:p>",
